{"tid":685604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真 Avenger3 Bug","createTime":"2018-05-31T14:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T13:56:31.000Z","uid":110564,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc5aa75f61e1faf86032b9e3c4e5bcaa19e1547","tid":685604,"uid":110564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:00:19.000Z","msg":"Thor拎到新武器 <br />\n而Stormbreaker應該只係擁有開啟彩虹橋嘅能力  <br />\n所以佢應該係睇唔到全個宇宙嘅地方發生咩事<br />\n(有能力瞬移但係睇唔到)<br />\n<br />\n但係佢一開彩虹橋就出現喺地球嘅戰場?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更加唔好講佢自己都唔知道Wakanda <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(black panther civil war先第一次出場，Thor已經唔喺地球，都冇地球人出現過同佢講有wakanda) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n*Hulk civil war都已經走咗，但係avg2佢喺地圖睇過wakanda個making <br />\n<br />\n如果咁講thor因為聽到hulk講個地方名就知喺邊， 或者好確實咁講咗地方位置出嚟，咁佢都要係因為見到嗰邊打緊先會飛過去啫<br />\n<br />\n咁如果只係電影情節冇交代到佢睇到晒個宇宙，點解見到都唔直接飛去泰坦星揾thanos，要去wakanda大叫bring me thanos!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/images/x9E5df\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fimages%2Fx9E5df&h=b9660fe9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a52f98c8ed1cf9426c70aca0dfe288bae06d0c47","tid":685604,"uid":110564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://goo.gl/images/x9E5df\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fimages%2Fx9E5df&h=b9660fe9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b09235726abce8842df8c595f65109c7043740b9","tid":685604,"uid":16120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:02:23.000Z","msg":"Noted with tha